Title: Artisan's Supply: Lava Beetles
Description:
Are you looking for work, herbalist? The Artisan's Consortium asked me to gather some beetles for their customers.

The land is plentiful, but not so much that I can simply step away and be back with their request.

But if you venture out, perhaps you could collect a few beetles on your way?
ObjectivesText: Deliver 5 Lava Beetles to Haephesta at the Ruby Lifeshrine.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Deliver 5 Lava Beetles to Haephesta at the Ruby Lifeshrine.
